## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="efdd1-103">Neste exemplo, um fluxo de trabalho é criado que consiste em um único <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> atividade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efdd1-103">In this example, a workflow is created that consists of a single <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> activity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efdd1-104">O <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> atividade tem um <xref:System.Activities.InArgument%601> chamado <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine.Text%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efdd1-104">The <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> activity has an <xref:System.Activities.InArgument%601> named <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine.Text%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efdd1-105">O aplicativo host cria uma instância do fluxo de trabalho e passa uma cadeia de caracteres, que mapeia para o <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine.Text%2A> argumento do <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> e é usado pelo <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> atividade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efdd1-105">The host application creates an instance of the workflow and passes a string, which maps to the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine.Text%2A> argument of the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> and is used by the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> activity.</span></span>  

```csharp  
Activity wf = new WriteLine();  

Dictionary<string, object> wfParams = new Dictionary<string, object>();  
wfParams.Add("Text", "Hello World!");  

WorkflowInvoker.Invoke(wf, wfParams);  

```
